net/mlx5e: Replace deprecated PCI_DMA_TODEVICE

The PCI API for DMA is deprecated, and PCI_DMA_TODEVICE is just defined
to DMA_TO_DEVICE for backward compatibility. Just use DMA_TO_DEVICE.

